title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Reno Air Races - Pre-release testing - Biplanes testing
description:
In this video we will have a look at the Reno Air race addon pre-release testing version which has been made available by Asobo on Friday. This time I used an aircraft from the biplanes category and played on my Xbox Series X which allowed me to record in 4K. 

Flying on the Xbox using the Xbox controller is a complete different experience. So next step is to find the most optimal settings so I can start winning some races.
